      "note": "Everything is possible and in Allah's power. His Plan is beneficent and allembracing. But it is not for His creatures to dictate to Him, or demand what He should do, or how He should do it. The Command is with Allah in all things. The Believers know His Omnipotence, and they also know that He will order His world for the best."
