      "note": "The meaning is that God grants man the freedom to choose between right and wrong: \"He guides unto Himself all who turn unto Him\" (verse 27 above) and \"are true to their bond with God\" (verse 20); on the other hand, He withholds His guidance from \"the iniquitous, who break their bond with \"God\" (2:26-27). See also the last sentence of 6:149 and the corresponding note 143."
